    {
      "start": 8.94,
      "end": 9.54,
      "text": "Yes."
    },
    {
      "start": 9.88,
      "end": 12.12,
      "text": "So the first performance was a disaster."
    },
    {
      "start": 12.32,
      "end": 15.84,
      "text": "But one person, a famous playwright, a director,"
    },
    {
      "start": 16.18,
      "end": 20.24,
      "text": "he liked the play and he wanted to direct it again."
    },
    {
      "start": 20.42,
      "end": 26.72,
      "text": "So he went to the Moscow Art Theater, which is a brand new fancy theater in Moscow."
    },
    {
      "start": 27.02,
      "end": 32.84,
      "text": "And in 1898, he put on the same play, The Seagull, and it got rave reviews."
    },
    {
      "start": 33.08,
      "end": 33.26,
      "text": "Really?"
    },
    {
      "start": 33.26,
